channel.title: Respawn-pk 317 [pi]
channel.description:
[size=36pt]ENJOY RESPAWN PK[/size]
[size=36pt]**WORKING ON V2**[/size]
Hope you guys enjoy this release, this server ran with 30+ for about a month i'm no longer hosting this. Maybe you make something really great out of this server!
-Features- -Dragon claws -Gambling -Skills work -Korasi -Statius -vesta -morrigans -zuriel -leechs arent as powerful as Turmoil -Pure command + master command -All emotes work -602 animations -Skill cape emotes all work -602 Anims/Gfx/ -Chaotics/Spirit Shields/PVP Armours -Tormented Demons -All skills working except Summoning and Hunter. -Almost every special works. -Good/Decent Economy if ran as is. -Pking/PvP. -Curse Prayers With Anims/Gfx/Effects -Clan Chat -Working SkillCape emotes. -All ancient spells work, all modern combat spells work, and Vengeance works. -Custom Quest Tab. -Lock EXP Tab. -PK Point/Slayer Points, and Shops for them. -Bosses like Jad, General Graardor, Kree, etc. -Minigames -Hp bar/10x Hit/Hitmarks Switching/Zoom A lot more just cant think of all of them.
